components.name: rails
components.description: Ruby on Rails is a full-stack web framework optimized for programmer happiness and sustainable productivity. It encourages beautiful code by favoring convention over configuration.

components.name: railties
components.description: Rails internals: application bootup, plugins, generators, and rake tasks.

components.name: activesupport
components.description: A toolkit of support libraries and Ruby core extensions extracted from the Rails framework. Rich support for multibyte strings, internationalization, time zones, and testing.

components.name: activestorage
components.description: Attach cloud and local files in Rails applications.

components.name: activerecord
components.description: Databases on Rails. Build a persistent domain model by mapping database tables to Ruby classes. Strong conventions for associations, validations, aggregations, migrations, and testing come baked-in.

components.name: activemodel
components.description: A toolkit for building modeling frameworks like Active Record. Rich support for attributes, callbacks, validations, serialization, internationalization, and testing.

components.name: activejob
components.description: Declare job classes that can be run by a variety of queuing backends.

components.name: actionview
components.description: Simple, battle-tested conventions and helpers for building web pages.

components.name: actiontext
components.description: Edit and display rich text in Rails applications.

components.name: actionpack
components.description: Web apps on Rails. Simple, battle-tested conventions for building and testing MVC web applications. Works with any Rack-compatible server.

components.name: actionmailer
components.description: Email on Rails. Compose, deliver, and test emails using the familiar controller/view pattern. First-class support for multipart email and attachments.

components.name: actionmailbox
components.description: Receive and process incoming emails in Rails applications.

components.name: actioncable
components.description: Structure many real-time application concerns into channels over a single WebSocket connection.
